law.history: Repealed 1958Ky. Acts ch. 77, Art. 10, sec. 10-102, effective July 1, 1960. -- Created 1956 Ky. Acts ch. 47, sec. 1, effective May 18, 1956.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Demand items other than for immediate payment over the counter, time within which bank may dishonor or refuse payment; credit given may be revoked, how.
